data.description: Nestled onto a large corner lot this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home offers a great combination of location and opportunity. This home is situated within minutes of the Dunedin Causeway, Honeymoon Island, shopping, restaurants, and schools. The Pinellas Trail is less than ½ mile away, while Hammock Park and Highlander Pool & Aquatic Center are directly across the street. It is in a highly desirable location. Upon approaching the home, notice the potential to make it your own around every corner. At the heart of this home lies the living room, kitchen, and dining room. The living room and dining room are spacious and welcoming. From the dining room step out to the Florida room - perfect for plant lovers - and enjoy your morning coffee. The kitchen features stainless appliances, garage access, and an additional eat-in dining area which could also be modified to enlarge the kitchen’s workspace. The primary bedroom is to the right of the living room. It features plenty of closet space and a private bathroom with a walk-in shower and a new vanity. The additional bedrooms are to the left of the living room. The common bathroom has been updated with fresh paint, a new vanity, and the bathtub has been reglazed. The majority of the home has received a fresh coat of paint. The large lot and fenced backyard have minimal landscaping and are awaiting your personal touch. This home has been witness to many memories and now welcomes you to make many more!
